cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.SE 

This paper is about a framework for machine learning models, with a focus on simplifying the process for practitioners and bringing the technology into production. The paper discusses the use of deep learning and provides a unifying Estimator interface, making it possible to write downstream infrastructure independent of the model implementation. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
